parameters:
Emma Thief Gang Member: I wonder if our message has reached
Nora?

Veteran Emma Thief Gang Member: What do you think of the
proposal from a man named Psema? I personally don't think
the leader would accept these conditions...

Emma Thief Gang Member: But it's necessary to save the Emma
Thief Gang! That's why we decided to secretly search for
Nora, hiding it from the leader--

Thief Nora: I-I found you...! Finally, we can meet. I'm so
glad, I'm so glad!

Veteran Emma Thief Gang Member: I never thought we would
actually meet... It was worth taking the risk and sending
requests to various places.

Thief Nora: I saw a request at the Adventurer's Guild! With
the help of my comrades, I was able to come here right away!

Emma Thief Gang Member: So you came from the Adventurer's
Guild... I see, so you've chosen that side.
Thief Nora: Huh... What do you mean?

Veteran Emma Thief Gang Member: It's well-known that Guild
Master Agonia and General Atu have a close relationship, and
it's General Atu who is moving the Imperial Army in the
campus...

Veteran Emma Thief Gang Member: It's a shame, Nora... We may
be willing to do it, but betraying the leader is a different
story!

Emma Thief Gang Member: Ugh... Strong... I can't believe
that crybaby Nora...

Thief Nora: I'm sorry for hurting you... but please listen,
it's an important matter!

Veteran Emma Thief Gang Member: Dragon's Eye...!? I heard
rumors about slaying a dragon, but I didn't know you were
involved too...
Thief Nora: I was with my comrades here!

Thief Nora: That's why we don't have to fight anymore! If we
sell the Dragon's Eye, we'll become rich and everything will
be fine!

Veteran Emma Thief Gang Member: I understand the situation.
Please come with me to the new hideout of the Emma Thief
Gang.

Veteran Emma Thief Gang Member: I apologize for my rude
remarks earlier.
Clea: No, it's okay. Can you take us with you too?

Veteran Emma Thief Gang Member: The leader should also want
to meet you. Let me guide you together.

\CL Area Liberation\c[18]\CL Campus Region/Emma Thief Gang
Hideout\c[0]

Clea: There's no one here. Are you sure this is really the
meeting place?

Thief Nora: *sniff sniff*... There's no mistake, the guild
leader is definitely here!

Thief Nora: Even if you can erase your presence, you can't
erase your scent.

Guild Leader Clevo: As expected, your sense of smell cannot
be deceived.
Thief Nora: Guild Leader! I'm glad to see you're doing well!

Thief Nora: Emma thieves... Are all the members of the Emma
Mercenary Corps doing well?

Guild Leader Clevo: Thanks to all of you, I'm doing well.
Let me express my gratitude once again.

Guild Leader Clevo: You should have seen the details of the
request.
Clea: Do you have any information?

Guild Leader Clevo: Other than the Oro's nobles... I have no
information at all.

Guild Leader Clevo: If you happen to come across any
information during your journey, please let me know. I will
also contact the Adventurer's Guild once I obtain any
information.
Thief Nora: W-Won't you search together with me...?

Guild Leader Clevo: It would be more efficient to split up
and move.

Guild Leader Clevo: Above all else... I am not qualified to
act together with you.

Thief Nora: Guild Leader... Please don't do anything
reckless...

Clea: Let's obtain information before Clevo-san, so that we
don't make any reckless decisions.

Mage Relm: Even so, Oro is a vast place, you know? There's
the Crystal Mine and many nobles reside there.

Priestess Sophia: There is a person who is perfect for
getting involved in wicked deeds.

Priestess Sophia: Even though I am far away from Oros, I
might know something about the organization called Mucos.
Clea: Yes, let's go meet Cors-san.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
Stolge of Affection: ...So you're really going, huh?

Clea: The pursuers of Rex have resumed their movement with
the army. We will go to battle alongside the Tarasa army.

Celis, the Gale: Even if it was only temporary that the
people of the Empire accepted us, who are their enemies,
during the subjugation of Rex...

Celis, the Gale: Risking our lives for their sake is what I
believe to be the way of the adventurer guild, Ftera.

Clea: I feel the same way. The wings of freedom should not
be broken by anyone.

Clea: Stolge-san, please go. Let each of us do what only we
can do.

Stolge of Affection: While Agonia is negotiating with the Senate,
I will continue to negotiate so that I can make contact with
important figures in Tarasa.

Stolge of Affection: ...Don't die, if you die before me, I won't
forgive you.
Celis, the Gale: Clea, do you have any regrets?

Clea: To be honest, I think there are regrets. But it's not
like I was forced to choose, it's a path I chose for myself.

Clea: I wanted to have tea together in the courtyard while
having trivial conversations with the people I met along the
way I have walked.
Celis, the Gale: Will you call me too?

Clea: Of course! Nora-san, Relm-san, and... Sophia-san too,
let's all go together.

Clea: It's a tea party while listening to the songs of
amateur minstrels.
Clea: I want it to be lively, with everyone laughing.
Clea: Hehe, it will definitely be fun.
Clea: Celis-san, let's fulfill our duty.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
